Sarah,

On behalf of the Westridge Department of Health Services, I am pleased to pro=
vide formal notice of award for Contract MSA-2021-114, emergency nurse staffi=
ng in support of the 2021 statewide respiratory surge response. The contract =
carries a ceiling of $2.0M with a term of March through September 2021.

Approved billing rates are RN $95/hr, LPN $68/hr, and CNA $42/hr, with lodgin=
g and per-diem reimbursable per the terms. Please note this contract is funde=
d in part by FEMA Public Assistance (75% federal), so documentation and rate =
compliance will be essential.

The fully executed award is attached (MSA-2021-114_Award.pdf). Please confirm=
 Meridian is prepared to begin onboarding no later than February 26, 2021.

Regards,

Robert Hale
Contract Administrator
Westridge Dept. of Health Services
(512) 555-0142

