Thank you for your inquiry regarding INV-0447. I have looked into it, and unf=
ortunately this invoice was denied and will not be paid.

There are two issues. First, the services dated July 4 fall under our last-da=
y-of-stay retroactive rule, which excludes those charges from reimbursement. =
Second, the invoice was submitted as a scanned image and missed the digital-s=
ubmission deadline required under the contract billing procedures.

